<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd" [ <!ENTITY rsquo "’"> <!ENTITY ndash "–"> ] ><html  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:ac="http://www.atlassian.com/schema/confluence/4/ac/" xmlns:ri="http://www.atlassian.com/schema/confluence/4/ri/" xml:lang="en" lang="en"><head><title>Blast Radius (Dictionary Entry)</title></head><body><ac:structured-macro ac:name="details" ac:schema-version="1" data-layout="default" ac:macro-id="2c14103c-f8a6-4d15-bcc9-f7312bbc0e2d"><ac:rich-text-body><table data-layout="default"><colgroup><col style="width: 153.0px;" /><col style="width: 573.0px;" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Contexts</strong></p></th><td><p>Cybersecurity, IAM</p></td></tr><tr><th><p><strong>Term</strong></p></th><td><p><strong>Blast Radius</strong></p></td></tr><tr><th><p><strong>Alternative Forms</strong></p></th><td><p>Entity Blast Radius, Identity Blast Radius</p></td></tr><tr><th><p><strong>Definitions</strong></p></th><td><p>The set of all privileges of an entity, considering hidden and transitive privileges. The blast radius provides the potential impact of the entity compromise. </p></td></tr></tbody></table></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ac:structured-macro ac:name="html-bobswift" ac:schema-version="1" data-layout="default" ac:macro-id="619ef746-3705-4337-861b-a372ddb39ee5"><ac:parameter ac:name="find">(PAGE_URL),(PAGE_TITLE)</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name="replace">$page_url,$page_title</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name="script">TECH:Social+Media+Toolbar^Social+Media+Toolbar.html</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro><h2>Quotes</h2><blockquote><p>BLAST RADIUS:</p><p>The full privileges of an entity in your cloud include hidden / transitive privileges.</p><p>(&hellip;) The full impact if an entity in your cloud is compromised.</p></blockquote><p style="text-align: right;">(<ac:link ac:card-appearance="inline"><ri:page